column1: SA1 Personal Income Summary: Personal Income, Population, Per Capita Personal Income
1/ Census Bureau midyear population estimate. Estimates for 2010-2015 reflect Census Bureau midyear state population estimates available as of December 2015.
2/ Per capita personal income is total personal income divided by total midyear population.
* Estimates prior to 1950 are not available for Alaska and Hawaii.
Note-- All dollar estimates are in current dollars (not adjusted for inflation).
Last updated: September 28, 2016-- revised estimates for 1998-2015.
